INSERT INTO `db_news`.`news` VALUES ('all','Daisy Mowke','Seven medical students have been suspended from a college in Tamil Nadu\'s Vellore over alleged ragging. A purported video of the incident, which happened at Christian Medical College, has been shared widely on social media. The video shows students being paraded half-naked inside the men\'s hostel and water being sprayed on them from a hose.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','00d52117fb8e4a6fa804fccabbc6e482','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668006931784_89.jpg?','https://www.timesnownews.com/education/tamil-nadu-cmc-vellore-suspends-7-medical-students-for-allegedly-ragging-1st-year-mbbs-students-article-95404768/amp?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','09:01 pm','Video shows students being paraded half-naked inside men\'s hostel in TN medical college','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/video-shows-students-being-paraded-halfnaked-inside-mens-hostel-in-tn-medical-college-1668007907443'),('all','Amartya Sharma','Actress Urvashi Dholakia said she\'s always categorised as a mother-of-two whenever she posts something on social media. She added, \"Why? Am I not an individual...then a mother of two kids? Does anyone say this to a man?\" This comes after Urvashi posted pictures on Instagram of herself in a bikini and penned a note on body positivity.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','07b94638f258453b9949e8089525c321','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668003405933_545.jpg?',NULL,'09:02 pm','Why am I categorised as mother-of-two? Am I not an individual?: Urvashi','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/why-am-i-categorised-as-motheroftwo-am-i-not-an-individual-urvashi-1668007951673'),('all','Indraneel Sen','The Supreme Court (SC) on Wednesday dismissed a public interest litigation (PIL) challenging the nomination of ex-Chief Justice of India (CJI) Ranjan Gogoi to Rajya Sabha. Petitioner Satish S Kambiye contended Gogoi was not eligible to be nominated. \"Who will decide the eligibility? You? Sorry, we don\'t find any merit in this plea,\" the SC bench said.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','0b110f2206764fd3b2b147e422a2cf0d','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668003007269_606.jpg?','https://theprint.in/india/sc-dismisses-plea-challenging-nomination-of-ex-cji-ranjan-gogoi-to-rajya-sabha/1206663/?amp=&utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','09:36 pm','SC dismisses PIL challenging ex-CJI Ranjan Gogoi\'s nomination to RS','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/sc-dismisses-pil-challenging-excji-ranjan-gogois-nomination-to-rs-1668009981412'),('all','Ambarish Awale','Global Dental Services (GDS), which operates the nationwide chain of oral care clinics Clove Dental, has raised $66 million in growth funding led by Bahrain-based Investcorp. Growth investor Tybourne Capital, as well as new and existing shareholders, also participated in the capital raising round. The investment is expected to fund GDS\' expansion to 1,000 clinics in the next five years.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','1d1449b16e5f41e3b1c7c68ccfa268a4','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668003217460_51.jpg?','https://yourstory.com/2022/11/global-dental-services-raises-66-million-led-by-in?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','09:33 pm','Global Dental Services raises $66 million in growth funding','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/global-dental-services-raises-$66-million-in-growth-funding-1668009834956'),('all','Indraneel Sen','Home Secretaries in nine states and District Magistrates in 31 districts are permitted to grant Indian citizenship to Hindus, Sikhs, Buddhists, Jains, Parsis and Christians coming from Afghanistan, Bangladesh and Pakistan. The Ministry of Home Affairs (MHA) said 1,414 people from these countries were given Indian citizenship from April 1 to December 