iness/nykaa-founder-falguni-nayar-at-htls-for-women-there-are-no-glass-ceilings-101667980920638-amp.html?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','09:32 pm','Recruited very young team members: Nykaa Founder Falguni Nayar','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/recruited-very-young-team-members-nykaa-founder-falguni-nayar-1668009734160'),('all','Dharini Mudgal','Chinese President Xi Jinping has warned the military that the country\'s national security is facing increased \"instability\" and \"uncertainty\", a report said. He instructed them to enhance capabilities to \"fight and win\" wars. \"The...military should devote all of its energy to...combat readiness, enhance its capability to fight and win, and...fulfil its missions and tasks in the new era,\" Xi said.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','526b2a9d68704b848ed9590145c21bf4','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668004974716_564.jpg?','https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/china-faces-instability-be-ready-to-fight-win-wars-xi-to-military-101667995123029-amp.html?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:59 pm','China faces instability, be ready to fight & win wars: Xi to military','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/china-faces-instability-be-ready-to-fight-win-wars-xi-to-military-1668007785044'),('all','Dharini Mudgal','Pakistan Finance Minister Ishaq Dar said that Asian Infrastructure Investment Bank (AIIB) will give $500 million to Pakistan as co-financing for a development program. The fund will be used for Asian Development Bank\'s Building Resilience with Active Countercyclical Expenditures (BRACE) program to counter the social fallouts of economic crisis. Dar said, \"The fund will be received in November.\"','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','59c52ddf28d8428a9e64e151d2055543','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668002314207_850.jpg?','https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/paki