larticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:57 pm','Ghazipur landfill trash dumped nearby to show height has come down: AAP','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/ghazipur-landfill-trash-dumped-nearby-to-show-height-has-come-down-aap-1668007636049'),('all','Swati Dubey','Karnataka government has called the circular by Pre University Education Department that directed colleges in Bengaluru to send students for PM Modi\'s rally on November 11 \'a mistake\' after withdrawing it on Tuesday. \"It was a mistake done by the DDPI (Deputy Director of Public Instruction) and we have initiated action against the official,\" Karnataka Education Minister BC Nagesh said.\n','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','7001d61ab81e437490f35c252bb02118','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668004848343_603.jpg?','https://www.hindustantimes.com/cities/bengaluru-news/a-mistake-karnataka-scraps-order-to-colleges-to-bring-students-for-pm-event-101667998798046-amp.html?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:20 pm','It was a mistake: Karnataka govt on circular to bring college students for PM event','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/it-was-a-mistake-karnataka-govt-on-circular-to-bring-college-students-for-pm-event-1668005422860'),('all','Amartya Sharma','Actress Julia Fox has said that she has noticed a shift in her acting career after dating rapper Kanye West. \"I\'m not getting as many offers as I was before, weirdly. There\'s been a lot of weird drawbacks with reaching that level of notoriety,\" she added. The duo dated briefly after Kim Kardashian filed for divorce from Kanye.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','a0488c231f4549af83e285aff6f047e6','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668007680665_142.jpg?','https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/hollywood/after-kanye-west-romance-julia-fox-reveals-shes-not-getting-as-many-acting-offers-as-before-1198194?amp=&utm_campaign=fullarti