al\' label began appearing on verified profiles in India on Wednesday. It appeared on the Twitter handles of PM Narendra Modi, Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman, Union Minister Amit Shah and others. According to Twitter, government accounts, commercial companies, business partners, major media outlets, publishers and some public figures will get the new \'Official\' label.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','a24f9d3ebe7147df91ff4e8536ee0fd5','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668008655713_574.jpg?','https://www.ptinews.com/news/business/twitter-adds-official-label-for-modi-some-verified-accounts/455111.html?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','09:25 pm','Twitter\'s new \'Official\' label starts appearing on verified accounts in India','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/twitters-new-official-label-starts-appearing-on-verified-accounts-in-india-1668009338060'),('all','Amartya Sharma','\'Bigg Boss 16\' contestant Archana Gautam has reportedly been evicted from the show after she got physically violent with co-contestant Shiv Thakare. As per a source, Archana tried to strangulate Shiv during a heated argument. \"The makers themselves saw the footage and took the fair decision of expelling Archana from the game for her violent actions,\" the source added.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','d8d84d545fff4b4888a8b7873fcc4661','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668004219561_58.jpg?','https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/amp/news/bollywood/archana-gautam-expelled-bigg-boss-16-gets-physically-violent-shiv-thakare/?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:47 pm','Archana Gautam evicted from \'Bigg Boss 16\' after getting violent: Report','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/archana-gautam-evicted-from-bigg-boss-16-after-getting-violent-report-1668007025789'),('all','Anmol Sharma','As per a police facts sheet released by a court, Sri Lanka cricketer Danushka Gunathilaka, who\'s under arrest in Australia on rape charges, met the victim through Tinder. Gunathilaka allegedly choked the Sydney woman thrice and also refused to wear condom. The woman underwent brain scan to check for any injury resulting from choking, the documents added.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','d95aad5e3b4b481399e7c2e6c06cddae','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668005786362_142.jpg?','https://www.crictracker.com/cricket-news/reports-danushka-gunathilaka-choked-sydney-woman-during-sexual-assault-which-pushed-her-to-take-brain-scan/?amp=1&utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:52 pm','Gunathilaka refused to wear condom, choked Tinder date 3 times: Court documents','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/gunathilaka-refused-to-wear-condom-choked-tinder-date-3-times-court-documents-1668007362173'),('all','Nidhi Sinha','Prime Minister Narendra Modi, BJP National President JP Nadda, Home Minister Amit Shah and other senior leaders arrived at the BJP\'s headquarters in Delhi on Wednesday for the party\'s Central Election Committee meeting. The meeting was held to finalise the party\'s candidates for the upcoming Gujarat Assembly elections. Gujarat Chief Minister Bhupendra Patel also attended the meeting.','09 Nov 2022,Wednesday','df3033c1b7914dd1bd0b01dcc6a6ccd3','https://static.inshorts.com/inshorts/images/v1/variants/jpg/m/2022/11_nov/9_wed/img_1668005314903_600.jpg?','https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1590328804605820929?utm_campaign=fullarticle&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=inshorts ','08:45 pm','PM Modi, Nadda attend BJP meet to finalise candidates for Gujarat polls','https://www.inshorts.com/en/news/pm-modi-nadda-attend-bjp-meet-to-finalise-candidates-for-gujarat-polls-1668006940105'),('all','Nidhi Sinha','The municipal corporation of Karnataka\'s Hubballi has granted permission to celebrate Tipu Jayanti and Kanakadasa Jayanti at Idgah Maidan on November 10 and 11 re